articles.title: Late Luis Suarez winner puts Atletico Madrid on brink of La Liga title - European round-up - Sky Sports
articles.description: Luis Suarez's 88th-minute winner against Osasuna has left Atletico Madrid on the brink of clinching the La Liga title for only the second time since 1996.
